_sText:
Oh no!  Hostage crisis in Venice!  Will the counter-terrorists be able to save the hostages before it's too late?!

Map Features:

. A boat you can hitch a ride on
. A cellar
. A house where the hostages are kept
. A market
. Custom nav
. Soundscape
. Some other stuff, go explore  : )

This is in beta stage, but I wanted to release it to get some feedback.  Up until now it has just been me and my buddies testing.  Hope you enjoy it, and please leave feedback!!  Thanks  : )

- Starving Hobo



NOTE:  I think the NAV file has been pakratted in, please leave a post if it isn't and I'll add it to the archive and re-upload.
